codex
Two concrete regressions have emerged in the normalization work: the detail model compares entered quantity against canonical allocated quantity, and MRP still interprets `quantity_ordered` in the entered UoM. I’m validating these against tests and checking whether cancellation’s claimed DB-faithful coverage actually exercises the action/snapshot/idempotency contract.
